        the present with the key words "doxazosin," "prazosin,"
        "terazosin," "adrenergic alpha-<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">antagonists</ENAMEX>," or "alpha
        <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">blocker</ENAMEX>." The search was then limited to clinical trials
