          (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">RR 1.19</NUMEX>, <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">95%</NUMEX> CI <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1.01</NUMEX>-<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1.40</NUMEX>). Since <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ALLHAT</ENAMEX> is a
          comparative trial, we know that doxazosin is associated
